    <section class="faq-section">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">What are the opening hours?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">The park is open every day from April to October, 9am to 7pm.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">How can I contact the park?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">You can contact us via the contact form on the Contact Us page.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">Is there parking available?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes, we have ample parking space available for all visitors.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">Are pets allowed in the park?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">Unfortunately, pets are not allowed in the park except for service animals.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Additional Questions -->
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">Are there any height restrictions for rides?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes, some rides have height restrictions for safety reasons. Please check the ride descriptions for details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">Can I purchase tickets online?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes, tickets can be purchased online through our website for your convenience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">Is there a lost and found service?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes, our lost and found service is located at the main entrance. Please visit or contact us if you lose an item.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2 class="faq-question">What dining options are available in the park?<span class="arrow"></span></h2>
                <p class="faq-answer">We have a variety of dining options, including fast food, sit-down restaurants, and snack bars throughout the park.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
